data.title: 准备以至少30秒的时间回答以下问题
data.answer: This picture gives information about an athlete swimmer who is preparing for a race or for training. He wears a white swimming cap. There are some words on this cap. He also wears a pair of swimming goggles. The swimming pool is quite clear. I think he must be very excited to start swimming. According to his ready position, he seems to be ready for backstroke. I believe that he is pretty good at this. Overall, this is an interesting picture.
